<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Build with Orb: AI Leaderboards</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --cream:#FBF8F0; --ink:#130F0B; --ink-mid:#5B5448; --ink-muted:#847E74; --ink-faint:#C4BFB8;
    --blue:#5B72FB; --blue-light:#AAEBFF; --green:#5F8A4D; --red:#DF4D33;
  }
  *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  body{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;background:var(--cream);color:var(--ink);min-height:100vh;position:relative;overflow-x:hidden}
  body::before{content:'';position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:420px;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 70% -10%,rgba(170,235,255,0.45),transparent);pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
  body::after{content:'';position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:360px;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 30% 110%,rgba(95,138,77,0.18),transparent);pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
  .container{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 32px 80px;position:relative;z-index:1}

  .header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:28px 0 40px}
  .logo{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:-1px}
  .header-badge{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.6px;text-transform:uppercase;background:rgba(91,114,251,0.12);color:var(--blue);padding:5px 12px;border-radius:20px}

  .hero{text-align:center;padding:20px 0 48px}
  .hero-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.6px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:12px}
  .hero h1{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:52px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:16px}
  .hero h1 span{color:var(--blue)}
  .hero p{font-size:16px;color:var(--ink-mid);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.6}

  .step-nav{display:flex;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);backdrop-filter:blur(4px);border:1px solid rgba(19,15,11,0.1);border-radius:12px;padding:6px;margin-bottom:32px}
  .step-pill{flex:1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;padding:10px 8px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-muted)}
  .step-pill.completed{color:var(--green);background:rgba(95,138,77,0.1)}
  .step-pill.active{color:var(--ink);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(19,15,11,0.1)}
  .step-pill.locked{opacity:0.38;cursor:not-allowed}
  .step-num{width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;background:rgba(19,15,11,0.08);color:var(--ink-muted);flex-shrink:0}
  .step-pill.active .step-num{background:var(--ink);color:var(--cream)}
  .step-pill.completed .step-num{background:var(--green);color:#fff}
  .step-label{display:none}
  @media(min-width:600px){.step-label{display:inline}}

  .card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.58);backdrop-filter:blur(6px);border:1px solid rgba(19,15,11,0.09);border-radius:12px;padding:32px;margin-bottom:24px;transition:border-color 0.2s,box-shadow 0.2s}
  .card:hover{border-color:rgba(19,15,11,0.16);box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(19,15,11,0.06)}
  .section-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.6px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px}
  .card h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.2}
  .card p{color:var(--ink-mid);line-height:1.65;font-size:14px}

  .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:var(--ink);color:var(--cream);border:none;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 24px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:opacity 0.15s,transform 0.1s;text-decoration:none}
  .btn:hover{opacity:0.85;transform:translateY(-1px)}
  .btn:active{transform:translateY(0)}
  .btn-outline{background:transparent;border:1.5px solid rgba(19,15,11,0.18);color:var(--ink)}
  .btn-outline:hover{background:rgba(19,15,11,0.04)}
  .btn-blue{background:var(--blue)}
  .btn-red{background:var(--red)}
  .btn-green{background:var(--green)}
  .btn-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:28px}
  .btn-row-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}

  .step-panel{display:none;animation:fadeIn 0.3s ease}
  .step-panel.active{display:block}
  @keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

  .slider-section{margin:28px 0 24px}
  .slider-labels{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:10px}
  .slider-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-muted);text-align:center;flex:1;transition:color 0.2s;cursor:pointer;padding:0 4px}
  .slider-label.active{color:var(--blue)}
  input[type=range]{-webkit-appearance:none;appearance:none;width:100%;height:4px;border-radius:99px;outline:none;cursor:pointer;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--blue) var(--fill),rgba(19,15,11,0.12) var(--fill))}
  input[type=range]::-webkit-slider-thumb{-webkit-appearance:none;width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue);border:3px solid var(--cream);box-shadow:0 1px 6px rgba(91,114,251,0.4);cursor:pointer;transition:transform 0.15s}
  input[type=range]::-webkit-slider-thumb:hover{transform:scale(1.15)}
  .slider-stop-dots{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 11px;margin-top:2px}
  .slider-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(19,15,11,0.15);transition:background 0.2s}
  .slider-dot.passed{background:var(--blue)}
  .metric-explain{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);border:1.5px solid rgba(91,114,251,0.22);border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin-top:16px}
  .metric-explain-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:8px}
  .metric-explain-icon{font-size:22px}
  .metric-explain-name{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:700}
  .metric-explain p{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-mid);line-height:1.65;margin:0}
  .spectrum-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:14px;padding:8px 14px;background:rgba(19,15,11,0.04);border-radius:8px;font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-muted)}
  .spectrum-bar span{font-weight:600}

  .endpoint-tabs{display:flex;border-bottom:1.5px solid rgba(19,15,11,0.1);margin-bottom:20px}
  .endpoint-tab{padding:10px 20px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink-muted);cursor:pointer;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;margin-bottom:-1.5px;transition:all 0.2s}
  .endpoint-tab.active{color:var(--ink);border-bottom-color:var(--red)}
  .code-block{background:var(--ink);border-radius:8px;padding:18px 20px;font-family:'Courier New',monospace;font-size:12px;color:#C8D0E0;line-height:1.7;overflow-x:auto;margin-bottom:16px}
  .code-keyword{color:var(--blue-light)}
  .code-string{color:#A8E8A0}
  .code-comment{color:#6A7090;font-style:italic}
  .code-key{color:#F0C880}
  .code-num{color:#F0A878}
  .response-block{background:rgba(95,138,77,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(95,138,77,0.25);border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;font-family:'Courier New',monospace;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.7;overflow-x:auto;max-height:220px;overflow-y:auto}
  .callout{border-radius:8px;padding:12px 16px;margin-top:12px}
  .callout-blue{background:rgba(91,114,251,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(91,114,251,0.18)}
  .callout-green{background:rgba(95,138,77,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(95,138,77,0.2)}
  .callout p{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-mid);margin:0;line-height:1.6}
  .callout-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px}
  .callout-blue .callout-title{color:var(--blue)}
  .callout-green .callout-title{color:var(--green)}

  .decision-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:14px;margin:20px 0 24px}
  @media(min-width:700px){.decision-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}}
  .decision-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);border:1px solid rgba(19,15,11,0.09);border-radius:10px;padding:16px}
  .decision-card:nth-child(1){border-top:3px solid var(--blue)}
  .decision-card:nth-child(2){border-top:3px solid var(--green)}
  .decision-card:nth-child(3){border-top:3px solid var(--red)}
  .decision-card:nth-child(4){border-top:3px solid var(--ink-faint)}
  .decision-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-bottom:6px}
  .decision-value{font-size:13px;font-weight:600}
  .decision-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-mid);margin-top:3px}
  .snippet-tabs{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:14px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .snippet-tab{padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;background:rgba(19,15,11,0.07);color:var(--ink-mid);transition:all 0.2s;border:none}
  .snippet-tab.active{background:var(--ink);color:var(--cream)}

  .lb-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px}
  .lb-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700}
  .date-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(19,15,11,0.06);color:var(--ink-mid);padding:5px 12px;border-radius:20px}
  .leaderboard-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px}
  .leaderboard-table th{text-align:left;padding:10px 16px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-muted);border-bottom:1.5px solid rgba(19,15,11,0.08)}
  .leaderboard-table td{padding:12px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(19,15,11,0.05)}
  .leaderboard-table tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}
  .leaderboard-table tr:hover td{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.45)}
  .place-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;background:rgba(19,15,11,0.07);color:var(--ink-muted)}
  .place-badge.gold{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(212,175,55,0.3),rgba(240,208,80,0.2));color:#9a7a08}
  .place-badge.silver{background:rgba(160,160,180,0.2);color:#5a5a7a}
  .place-badge.bronze{background:rgba(176,125,80,0.2);color:#7a4820}
  .tag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:6px;vertical-align:middle;letter-spacing:0.3px}
  .tag-gold{background:rgba(212,175,55,0.2);color:#9a7a08}
  .tag-blue{background:rgba(91,114,251,0.14);color:var(--blue)}
  .tag-red{background:rgba(223,77,51,0.14);color:var(--red)}

  .gamify-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;margin-top:24px}
  @media(max-width:600px){.gamify-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .gamify-card{border-radius:10px;padding:20px;text-align:center}
  .gamify-card:nth-child(1){background:rgba(95,138,77,0.09);border:1px solid rgba(95,138,77,0.22)}
  .gamify-card:nth-child(2){background:rgba(212,175,55,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.25)}
  .gamify-card:nth-child(3){background:rgba(223,77,51,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(223,77,51,0.2)}
  .gamify-icon{font-size:28px;margin-bottom:8px}
  .gamify-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:5px}
  .gamify-desc{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--ink-mid);line-height:1.5}

  .awards-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;margin-bottom:28px}
  @media(max-width:600px){.awards-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .award-card{border-radius:10px;padding:20px;text-align:center}
  .award-card.king{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(212,175,55,0.16),rgba(240,210,80,0.09));border:1px solid rgba(212,175,55,0.32)}
  .award-card.mover{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(91,114,251,0.12),rgba(91,114,251,0.06));border:1px solid rgba(91,114,251,0.25)}
  .award-card.battle{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(223,77,51,0.1),rgba(223,77,51,0.05));border:1px solid rgba(223,77,51,0.24)}
  .award-emoji{font-size:34px;margin-bottom:8px}
  .award-title{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:6px}
  .award-winner{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px}
  .award-desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-mid)}
  .award-card.king .award-title{color:#9a7a08}
  .award-card.mover .award-title{color:var(--blue)}
  .award-card.battle .award-title{color:var(--red)}
  .awards-logic-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px;margin-bottom:28px}
  @media(max-width:600px){.awards-logic-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}

  .progress-item{margin-bottom:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);border:1px solid rgba(19,15,11,0.08);border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px}
  .progress-header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:10px}
  .progress-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:600}
  .progress-meta{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-muted)}
  .progress-bar-track{height:8px;background:rgba(19,15,11,0.08);border-radius:99px;overflow:hidden}
  .progress-bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:99px}
  .progress-label{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:6px;font-size:10px;color:var(--ink-muted)}

  .prereq-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;margin-bottom:28px}
  @media(max-width:600px){.prereq-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .prereq-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);border:1px solid rgba(19,15,11,0.09);border-radius:10px;padding:20px}
  .prereq-icon{font-size:22px;margin-bottom:10px}
  .prereq-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px}
  .prereq-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-mid);line-height:1.6}

  .download-box{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(91,114,251,0.08),rgba(91,114,251,0.04));border:1.5px solid rgba(91,114,251,0.22);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;text-align:center}
  .download-box h3{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}
  .download-box p{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-mid);max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 20px;line-height:1.6}

  .divider{border:none;border-top:1px solid rgba(19,15,11,0.08);margin:24px 0}
  code{background:rgba(19,15,11,0.07);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;font-family:'Courier New',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--blue)}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">orb</div>
    <div class="header-badge">Interactive Demo</div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-label">Build with Orb</div>
    <h1>AI <span>Leaderboards</span></h1>
    <p>Track who's adopting your AI product, motivate your team, and share progress — powered by Orb's usage billing infrastructure.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="step-nav" id="stepNav">
    <div class="step-pill active" onclick="goToStep(0)" id="pill-0"><div class="step-num">1</div><span class="step-label">Track</span></div>
    <div class="step-pill locked" id="pill-1"><div class="step-num">2</div><span class="step-label">Call</span></div>
    <div class="step-pill locked" id="pill-2"><div class="step-num">3</div><span class="step-label">Build</span></div>
    <div class="step-pill locked" id="pill-3"><div class="step-num">4</div><span class="step-label">Review</span></div>
    <div class="step-pill locked" id="pill-4"><div class="step-num">5</div><span class="step-label">Pizzaz</span></div>
    <div class="step-pill locked" id="pill-5"><div class="step-num">6</div><span class="step-label">Ship</span></div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 1 -->
  <div class="step-panel active" id="step-0">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="section-label" style="color:var(--red)">Step 1 — Track</div>
      <h2>What does great adoption look like?</h2>
      <p>Before you build, decide which signal matters most to your team. This becomes your leaderboard metric — the single number that captures who's getting the most value from your AI product.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:14px">Like billable metrics, you should match this to how your customers understand value. Keeping your leaderboard metric close to how you bill makes calculations easy — but less technical users may not grasp how it translates to real outcomes. There's a spectrum.</p>

      <div class="slider-section">
        <div class="slider-labels">
          <div class="slider-label" onclick="setSlider(0)" id="slabel-0">Tokens</div>
          <div class="slider-label active" onclick="setSlider(1)" id="slabel-1">Credits</div>
          <div class="slider-label" onclick="setSlider(2)" id="slabel-2">Work Output</div>
          <div class="slider-label" onclick="setSlider(3)" id="slabel-3">Outcomes</div>
        </div>
        <div style="padding:8px 0">
          <input type="range" id="metricSlider" min="0" max="3" value="1" step="1" oninput="onSlider(this.value)" style="--fill:33%">
        </div>
        <div class="slider-stop-dots">
          <div class="slider-dot passed" id="dot-0"></div>
          <div class="slider-dot passed" id="dot-1"></div>
          <div class="slider-dot" id="dot-2"></div>
          <div class="slider-dot" id="dot-3"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-explain">
          <div class="metric-explain-header">
            <div class="metric-explain-icon" id="explainIcon">🪙</div>
            <div class="metric-explain-name" id="explainName">Credits</div>
          </div>
          <p id="explainText">The current gold standard in AI pricing. Credits are simpler to understand because they often translate to costs. But less technical teams may still not fully understand how this translates — and tracking the metric you bill on can give the impression that users are racking up costs rather than value.</p>
          <div class="spectrum-bar">
            <span>← Easy for your team</span>
            <span style="color:rgba(19,15,11,0.18)">·····</span>
            <span>Easy for users →</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>For this dashboard, we'll keep it simple and go with <strong>Credits</strong> — the most common starting point for AI products.</p>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="btn btn-outline" style="visibility:hidden">← Back</button>
        <button class="btn" onclick="nextStep()">🪙 Pick Credits Used →</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 2 -->
  <div class="step-panel" id="step-1">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="section-label" style="color:var(--blue)">Step 2 — Call</div>
      <h2>Pull the data you need from Orb</h2>
      <p>The leaderboard requires two sequential API calls — first to discover your license types, then to query per-user usage for each one. Both use cursor-based pagination and <code>YYYY-MM-DD</code> date params.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:24px">
        <div class="endpoint-tabs">
          <div class="endpoint-tab active" onclick="switchEndpoint(this,'lic')">① GET /license_types</div>
          <div class="endpoint-tab" onclick="switchEndpoint(this,'usage')">② GET /licenses/usage</div>
        </div>

        <div id="ep-lic">
          <p style="font-size:13px;margin-bottom:16px">List all license types for your account. Required first step — the usage endpoint needs a <code>license_type_id</code>. Each type has an <code>id</code>, <code>name</code>, and <code>grouping_key</code>. Most accounts have one (e.g. "AI Seat"). If yours has several, the pipeline fetches usage for each and sums credits per user.</p>
          <div class="code-block"><span class="code-keyword">GET</span> https://api.withorb.com/v1/license_types?limit=100
Authorization: Bearer <span class="code-string">{ORB_API_KEY}</span></div>
          <div class="response-block">{"data":[{"id":"lt_abc123","name":"AI Seat","grouping_key":"user_id"}],"pagination_metadata":{"has_more":false,"next_cursor":null}}</div>
          <div class="callout callout-blue" style="margin-top:12px">
            <p class="callout-title">Why this step exists</p>
            <p>There's no way to query all usage without knowing your type IDs first. Fetching license types upfront also future-proofs the pipeline: add a second tier later and the loop handles it automatically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="ep-usage" style="display:none">
          <p style="font-size:13px;margin-bottom:4px">Fetch per-license credit consumption for a date range. Run once per license type, per time window. The leaderboard makes <strong>three parallel fetches</strong> per page load: current week, previous week (rank change), and Jan 1 → today (Q1 progress).</p>
          <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-muted);margin-bottom:16px">Key: <code>external_license_id</code> = display name, <code>consumed_credits</code> = usage value.</p>
          <div class="code-block"><span class="code-keyword">GET</span> https://api.withorb.com/v1/licenses/usage
  ?subscription_id=<span class="code-string">{ORB_SUBSCRIPTION_ID}</span>
  &license_type_id=<span class="code-string">lt_abc123</span>
