## Orb API — Complete Specification

**Base URL:** \`https://api.withorb.com/v1\`

> ⚠️ The HTML demo used \`api.billwithorb.com\` — that is fictional. The real base URL is \`api.withorb.com\`.

### Call 1: List License Types

\`\`\`
GET /license_types?limit=100
Authorization: Bearer {ORB_API_KEY}
\`\`\`

Paginate with \`cursor\` until \`pagination_metadata.next_cursor\` is null.

Response shape:
\`\`\`json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "lt_abc123",
      "name": "AI Seat",
      "grouping_key": "user_id"
    }
  ],
  "pagination_metadata": {
    "has_more": false,
    "next_cursor": null
  }
}
\`\`\`

You need the \`id\` from each license type to make Call 2. This is a required prerequisite.

