### Call 2: Get Usage for All Licenses of a Type

\`\`\`
GET /licenses/usage?subscription_id={SUB_ID}&license_type_id={LT_ID}&start_date={YYYY-MM-DD}&end_date={YYYY-MM-DD}&group_by=license&limit=100
Authorization: Bearer {ORB_API_KEY}
\`\`\`

**Required query params:**
- \`subscription_id\` — from \`ORB_SUBSCRIPTION_ID\` env var
- \`license_type_id\` — from Call 1
- \`start_date\` — \`YYYY-MM-DD\` format (NOT ISO datetime)
- \`end_date\` — \`YYYY-MM-DD\` format (NOT ISO datetime)
- \`group_by=license\` — required to get per-license breakdown
- \`limit=100\`

Paginate with \`cursor\` until \`pagination_metadata.next_cursor\` is null.

Response shape:
\`\`\`json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "license_id": "lic_xyz",
