**Key field mappings — do not get these wrong:**
| Purpose | Field to use |
|---|---|
| Credits used | \`consumed_credits\` (NOT \`credits_used\`) |
| User display name | \`external_license_id\` (NOT \`display_name\`) |
| Stable user key | \`external_license_id ?? license_id\` |

